import React from 'react'; import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles'; import TextField from '@material-ui/core/TextField'; import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button'; import FormControl from '@material-ui/core/FormControl'; import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography'; const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({ root: { '& .MuiTextField-root': { margin: theme.spacing(1), width: '25ch', }, }, btn:{ margin: theme.spacing(6) } })); const ABMMedicoForm = ({ }) => { const classes = useStyles(); const [value, setValue] = React.useState('Controlled'); const [values, setValues] = useState({ nombre: '', appellidos: '', dni: '', email: '', mobilePhone: '', }); const handleChange = (prop) => (event) => { setValues({ ...values, [prop]: event.target.value }); }; const handleClickShowPassword = () => { setValues({ ...values, showPassword: !values.showPassword }); }; return (
); } export default ABMMedicoForm;
